column3: “Wow! Is all I can say about this strain. Smooth , yet quick relaxation hit my joints and head. Goodnights sleep comes as well!”

“This Strain gave me the best head change I've had in awhile. Plus, the high wasn't overwhelming to where I was dumbfounded. Surprisingly it made me wanna get up and get stuff done....

I highly recommend the Manitoba Poison Strain anytime I wanna get things taken care of.”
“I have Manitoba wreck that hits heavy!!!!!👋🏿👋🏿👋🏿👋🏿👋🏿👋🏿👋🏿👋🏿”
“Manitoba Poison hits smooth off a pipe, joint or bong. I recommend that you try to get your hands on this strain if you can and test it out.”
